                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-924" type="surname" value="PAINE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350406-name-924" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE PAINE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant E</hi> 1.) I secured the prisoner, and have the coat.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I heard somebody sing out "Stop thief," I ran, and they took me.</p>
               <p>(Thomas Higgs, a coach-trimmer, of New Compton-street, and Ann Lepey, gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
